00:50:04,034 --> 00:50:09,039
was the one that I could often
be more vulnerable with.

1214
00:50:09,122 --> 00:50:10,707
There's always been something
that's like,

1215
00:50:10,790 --> 00:50:12,208
I don't know, a kinship.

1216
00:50:12,292 --> 00:50:14,628
Nothing has ever, ever, ever,
ever happened

1217
00:50:14,711 --> 00:50:16,171
<i>romantically with us.</i>

