00:53:21,773 --> 00:53:23,149
That's my boy!

1285
00:53:23,233 --> 00:53:25,819
[sobbing]

1286
00:53:25,902 --> 00:53:28,822
That's my boy!
[Harry sobbing]

1287
00:53:28,905 --> 00:53:31,866
<i>Suddenly, something
completely unexpected</i>

1288
00:53:31,950 --> 00:53:34,452
<i>and serious happens,</i>

