00:53:38,248 --> 00:53:39,374
It's about death.

1291
00:53:39,457 --> 00:53:40,834
<i>It's such a massive scene</i>

1292
00:53:40,917 --> 00:53:42,418
<i>'cause it is also
the first time</i>

