00:53:54,597 --> 00:53:59,018
He's back, he's back.
Voldemort's back.

1299
00:53:59,102 --> 00:54:01,271
<i>The moment of
Cedric Diggory's death</i>

1300
00:54:01,354 --> 00:54:05,817
<i>is the moment
